Class Enquiry

java.lang.Object
enquiry.Repliable
enquiry.Enquiry
public class Enquiry extends Repliable
The Enquiry class represents an inquiry made by an applicant regarding a BTO project. It extends the Repliable class, inheriting functionality related to replies. Each enquiry has a question and can have a corresponding reply.
